			<div id="pagetitle">
				<h1>General Preferences</h1>
			</div>
			
			<ul>
				<li><strong>File erasing level:</strong> Select the security level for erasing data from a hard drive.  Available options are Simple (1 pass), DoD (7 passes), and Gutmann (35 passes).</li>
				<li><strong>CD/DVD erasing level:</strong> Select the security level of erasing data from a rewritable optical disc.  Available options are Quick and Complete.</li>
				<li><strong>Warn before erasing:</strong> Display an alert dialog to warn the user about the files which are about to be erased.  </li>
				<li><strong>Play sounds:</strong> Play sounds when Permanent Eraser is complete.</li>
			</ul>
			
			<div id="taskbox">
				<p><strong>Tip:</strong> Holding down the Option key when Permanent Eraser starts will temporarily disable the warnings for that session.</p>
			</div>
			
			
			<h2 class="seealso">See also</h2>
			<p class="seealso"><a href = "erasing-levels.html">Erasing levels</a></p>

